== Notable people ==

=== Born in Debrecen ===
* Emma Adler (1858–1935), writer
* Lorenzo Alvary (1909–1996), operatic bass
* Ferenc Barnás (born 1959), novelist
* Zsolt Baumgartner (born 1981), first Hungarian Formula One driver
* Mihály Csokonai Vitéz (1773–1805), poet
